headline: Interactive Brokers Expands Global Reach with Ljubljana Stock Exchange Access
summary: GREENWICH, Conn., March 11, 2025--Interactive Brokers (Nasdaq: IBKR) announced today that it has expanded its market offerings by adding access to the Ljubljana Stock Exchange.
